{"tid":902200,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"路過慕尼黑，哥迪奧拿拜訪拜仁","createTime":"2018-11-14T15:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T07:42:58.000Z","uid":143284,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7bf6c8e2a2686046e7a578dfb95b7dbd3f94ed46","tid":902200,"uid":143284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:35:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bild.de/sport/fussball/fussball/bayern-muenchen-darum-besucht-trainer-pep-guardiola-seinen-alten-klub-58422180.bild.html#fromWall\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bild.de%2Fsport%2Ffussball%2Ffussball%2Fbayern-muenchen-darum-besucht-trainer-pep-guardiola-seinen-alten-klub-58422180.bild.html%23fromWall&d=d7VJPFS6CXfBo3B1q4wvF0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=2b163033\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bild.de/sport/fussball/fussball/bayern-muenchen-darum-besucht-trainer-pep-guardiola-seinen-alten-klub-58422180.bild.html#fromWall</a> 圖片報<br />\n<br />\n據德國媒體《圖片報》報導，前拜仁慕尼黑主帥哥迪奧拿本週三出現在了前東家拜仁慕尼黑的訓練場塞貝納大街。報導稱當地時間週三上午11:20，哥迪奧拿來到了拜仁慕尼黑俱樂部。當時拜仁主教練尼高&middot;高華正在帶隊訓練。<br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿曾經在2013-2016年執教拜仁慕尼黑，他帶領拜仁慕尼黑獲得三次德甲冠軍以及兩次德國杯冠軍。那麼這次哥迪奧拿為什麼回到塞貝納大街？<br />\n據《圖片報》的消息，哥迪奧拿要前往巴塞羅那，正好在慕尼黑停留。借此機會他來到拜仁慕尼黑俱樂部，看望拜仁的朋友。另外哥迪奧拿也和拜仁慕尼黑主席漢尼斯保持著聯繫，同時他在慕尼黑還有一處住處。"},{"pid":"3e7510ecdadeb82934857574ded64288ece84a64","tid":902200,"uid":4203,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"諗起以前成日有人屌 哥帥拜仁都教到咁廢<br />\n要佢去英超證明自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca8531c7d47576f0055b2b74966470ac8f318c1","tid":902200,"uid":194415,"like":53,"dislike":16,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"3e7510ecdadeb82934857574ded64288ece84a64","tid":902200,"uid":4203,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"諗起以前成日有人屌 哥帥拜仁都教到咁廢<br />\n要佢去英超證明自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/